race.comment: TURNAQUID (3) closed off strongly from well back last start at Wodonga, finishing fourth. Rock-hard fit now and looks tough to hold out. WANNABEAPOODLE (4) resumes over his pet trip and is already a winner here. Carries a big weight but draws kindly and deserves his chance. LOCO FOR COCO (10) doesn't win often but was good last time at Yea, finishing third. Faces a stronger field but on her best form she can test these. MAGNEA (9) improved last start when beaten under 2L at Wangaratta after racing on speed. In the mix off that. THE CUBAN (5) was better last start at Tatura and is open to further improvement on the quick back-up. An inside draw helps.
